data.description: THIS ONE IS A MUST SEE! Spacious 3/3 located in the desirable Sebring Hills area. The living room features classic tray ceilings with crown molding and kitchen is a chef's dream with rich wood cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless appliances and a handy eat-at bar with stools included. A huge master suite is complete with his and hers walk-in closets, and bath with double vanities, relaxing jetted garden tub and a roomy step-in shower. The split plan includes a second bedroom with its own bath, great privacy for your visitors or teens, third bedroom and additional bath. Bonus room would make a perfect office, craft room or could be converted into a fourth bedroom if needed. Home was built with ICF construction for strength and energy savings, roof was replaced in 2018 and a/c & ductwork in 2020. Surround sound system and cameras convey with sale. Make your appointment to take a look today!
